    "According to research, semantic similarity can be classified into corpus-based similarity and knowledge-based similarity (Gomaa & Fahmy, 2013).",
    "Due to the lack of publicly available corpora for technical text data, specifically maintenance related data, we consider a pre-trained sentence transformer model.",
    "Transformer models are basically encoder-decoder models.",
    "The task of the encoder is to take an input of raw text and map it to a numerical sequence.",
    "The decoder then uses the output of the encoder along with other contextual information to generate a meaningful output (Vaswani et al., 2017)."
